  "texts": [
    "An example may be the regulation of nuclear weapons.",
    "The technology is available and there are incentives favoring their use, but they are-globally-not deployed.",
    "This has been achieved through international agreements.",
    "However, on second thought, the analogy between nuclear weapons and AI doesn't necessarily inspire confidence.",
    "Large-scale nuclear weapons have been used in the past, even if it was a long time ago."
